Done. Feature #4 "Dream quality scorer" is implemented and committed.

**What was built:**

- **`prompts/dreams/quality_score_prompt.txt`** — LLM prompt template for scoring dreams on 4 dimensions (coherence 30%, identity_consistency 30%, novelty 20%, non_repetition 20%)
- **`src/svapna/dream/score.py`** — Scorer module following the same patterns as `consolidate/score.py`: `DreamScorerConfig` (loads from `.ai/models.yml`), `DreamScore`/`QualityDimensions` dataclasses, `score_dream()` with retry logic, `score_batch()` for bulk scoring, and `filter_by_quality()` to gate training data
- **`tests/test_dream_score.py`** — 22 tests covering all 4 test cases plus error handling, formatting, config loading, and edge cases

All 125 tests pass (103 existing + 22 new). Feature status updated in `feature_list.json` (4/12 completed).
